# Background-music files. The panel ships with an empty manifest +
# README in apps/web/public/audio/, but the audio itself is the user's
# responsibility — C418 / Lena Raine retain rights to the actual
# Minecraft tracks, so bundling them in a public repo would be
# redistribution without licence. Drop your own files in the dir
# locally; git won't track them.
apps/web/public/audio/*.mp3
apps/web/public/audio/*.ogg
apps/web/public/audio/*.wav
apps/web/public/audio/*.m4a
apps/web/public/audio/*.flac
apps/web/public/audio/*.aac
